dc_description_s: This data represents roads for Vernon County, Wisconsin in 2024. [This data set consists of digital map files containing road centerline information obtained predominantly by heads up digitizing off of ortho imagery, and through previously created datasets maintained by Vernon County. Features contained in the data set include road centerlines countywide and associated attributes and annotation.]
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison.
